      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPRING CRUISER (8) has a strong record this track and trip including two wins from three starts. In the money last time at this track (22.97) in a Grade 5, finishing a 3.5 lengths third. With a clean break looks hard to beat. QUEEN CARAMEL (3) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth at this track, but was among the placings at Richmond Straight three back. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the low draw. Can improve sharply here. HOUDINI ESCAPE (2) is rarely out of the finish, recording eight places from 15 starts. Finished in the money last time though when second (22.58) at Gosford. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Must be included in calculations. TAP OUT BOSTON (4) can measure up with the right run.",
